	* SoObjects/Mailer/SOGoMailAccount.m ([SOGoMailAccount
	-lookupFolder:ofClassNamed:inContext:]): added the ability to
	configure the name of the SOGoDraftFolders with the ud var
	"SOGoDraftsFolderName".

